{"tid":2300512,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"是超靚食得 日式叉燒","createTime":"2020-11-25T14:50:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-15T13:20:57.000Z","uid":194483,"like":62,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"7934cfb11bdbf15c0994a993624624b1eecb1ba3","tid":2300512,"uid":194483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T14:50:35.000Z","msg":"尋日製作過程重溫<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2299018\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2299018</a><br />\n今日終於食得<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XdG4s5n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXdG4s5n.jpg&h=ef57bed5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iYWTmqm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiYWTmqm.jpg&h=f1810931&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cZnOULk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcZnOULk.jpg&h=f81e1cb0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KY7Z1qj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKY7Z1qj.jpg&h=0e429d95&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1ZbHeLi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1ZbHeLi.jpg&h=389ccec7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n切開好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n煎香<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nd脂香<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n送啤酒一流<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />（屋企冇啤酒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n今次煮左1.5個鐘，下次試下2個鐘，等佢入口即溶<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee2effec4b87fa5bbbe0be